    image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMTIiIGhlaWdodD0iMTIiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAxMiAxMiIgZmlsbD0ibm9uZSIgeG1sbnM9Imh0dHA6Ly93d3cudzMub3JnLzIwMDAvc3ZnIj4KPHBhdGggZD0iTTIgNEw2IDhMMTAgNCIgc3Ryb2tlPSIjNkM3NTdEIiBzdHJva2Utd2lkdGg9IjEuNSIgc3Ryb2tlLWxpbmVjYXA9InJvdW5kIiBzdHJva2UtbGluZWpvaW49InJvdW5kIi8+Cjwvc3ZnPgo=);
}

QHeaderView::section {
    background-color: #F1F3F4;
    border: 1px solid #CED4DA;
    color: #6C757D;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Arial', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* Cards */
QFrame[class="card"] {
    background-color: white;
    border: 1px solid #E9ECEF;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px;
}

QFrame[class="card-shadow"] {
    background-color: white;
    border: 1px solid #E9ECEF;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px;
    /* QSS doesn't support box-shadow, will handle in Python */
}

/* Dividers */
QFrame[class="divider"] {
    background-color: #E9ECEF;
    max-height: 1px;
    min-height: 1px;
    border: none;
}

/* Status Badges */
QLabel[class="badge"] {
    background-color: #4A90E2;
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: white;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    text-align: center;
}

QLabel[class="badge-success"] {
    background-color: #28A745;
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: white;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    text-align: center;
}

QLabel[class="badge-warning"] {
    background-color: #FFC107;
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: #212529;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    text-align: center;
}

QLabel[class="badge-error"] {
    background-color: #DC3545;
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: white;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    text-align: center;
}

/* Tool Tips */
QToolTip {
    background-color: #212529;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: white;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Arial', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
}